#

Pork Gravy with Parmesan and Aromatic Herbs

$15.99
250 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Comfort FoodSavoryGourmet

Description

Rich and savory pork gravy infused with aromatic herbs and topped with grated Parmesan for a luxurious touch.

Ingredients

  • Pork drippings: 1 cup
  • All-purpose flour: 3 tablespoons
  • Chicken broth: 2 cups
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Fresh thyme: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • Fresh rosemary: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
